title: American horror story :Satan meets The Angel of Death - Asylum
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment:
“I was invited, unlike you.” 

This line sums up one of my family reunions.
How can the angel of death be so beautiful and comforting.
I miss this AHS. The newer seasons are okay, a little too much drama rather than horror, but season 2 put the Horror in American Horror Story.

Her character is morbidly beautiful. the soft almost like a caring mothers tone of voice reassuring everything will be fine. the phrase "kiss of death" being visually portrayed, the wings and the black veil worn normally for a funeral. The character, Asylum and Coven have always been a high marker for me. I'm not to sure on Roanoke still but I plan on buying it just like I did with the others.
